<BaseLayout title="Research & Analysis - Non-Code Uses">
<div class="breadcrumbs">
  <div class="breadcrumbs-inner">
    <a href="/">Index</a><span class="bc-sep">/</span>
    <a href="/ideas/non-code/">Non-Code Uses</a><span class="bc-sep">/</span>
    <span class="bc-current">Research &amp; Analysis</span>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="subpage-hero">
  <div class="subpage-hero-inner">
    <div>
      <h1>Research and Analysis</h1>
      <p>Deep research templates, OSINT investigation, and structured analysis workflows.</p>
    </div>
    <img class="subpage-hero-img" src="/images/research.png" alt="Research illustration">
  </div>
</div>
<div class="page">
  <p>The <a class="repo-link" href="/?category=research">Research</a> category is one of the largest in the index. The <a class="repo-link" href="/repos/claude-deep-research-template-implementation-template/">Claude Deep Research Template</a> provides a structured approach to multi-source research, while the <a class="repo-link" href="/repos/claude-stack-research-workspace/">Claude Stack Research Workspace</a> focuses on technology evaluation.</p>
  <p><a class="repo-link" href="/repos/claude-dork/">Claude Dork</a> generates search queries (dorks) across multiple platforms for OSINT-style research. <a class="repo-link" href="/repos/claude-osint-investigator/">Claude OSINT Investigator</a> takes this further with a full open-source intelligence workspace.</p>
  <div style="margin-top: 2rem;"><a href="/?category=research" style="font-weight: 500;">Browse all Research repositories &rarr;</a></div>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
